<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="529">Notes Roy. Bot. Gard. Edinburgh</emphasis>
32: 353. 1973), who indicated 989.49, 989.50 and 989.51 (LINN) as types. The same authors (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="529">Bot. J. Linn. Soc.</emphasis>
82: 245, 253. 1981) designated 989.48 as 
<typeStatus pageNumber="529">lectotype</typeStatus>
, but this collection lacks the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="529">
<volumeTitle pageNumber="529">Species Plantarum</volumeTitle>
</emphasis>
number (i.e. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“27”" pageNumber="529">&quot;27&quot;</normalizedToken>
), was a post-1753 addition to the collection, and is not original material for the name.
</paragraph>
